### ğŸ“ Example Query

```sql
SELECT
    start_station_name,
    end_station_name,
    COUNT(*) AS trip_count,
    AVG(trip_duration_sec) AS avg_duration
FROM gold.trips_2021
GROUP BY start_station_name, end_station_name
ORDER BY trip_count DESC;
